<bibRefCitation author="Chandler, P. J." box="[416,621,1996,2022]" pageId="29" refId="ref41753" refString="Chandler, P. J. (2004 a) Fauna Europaea: Mycetophilidae. In: De Jong, H. (Ed), Fauna Europaea: Diptera, Nematocera. Fauna Europaea version 1.1, available at http: // www. faunaeur. org [accessed September 2009 as version 1.3 of April 19 th 2007.]" type="url" year="2004">Chandler (2004a)</bibRefCitation>
